Summary: driving to the gym when i looked up and i saw 'see through' metallic objects fluttering inteh skyn going left and right and disappearing and reappering and finally disappering
divs: Sighting DetailsValentine's day 2009 at 0900, i was driving to the gym when i looked up at a stoplight. i saw what looked like 30 or 40 mettalic and see-through fluttering wings. they looked liked a flock of birds but they were not. these were metallic and kept going left and right. they were in formation, like one was a leader and the rest following. they also disappeared and reappeared. it was a sunny morning with some clouds. i stared at the fluttering objects for a good 15 seconds before it finally disappeared. they were probably about a hundred feet up in the air. again, these were not birds; they reminded me of a cross between crystals and something of a metallic nature. when the disappeared, it wasn't all at once, it was gradual disappearce within a spand of 2-3 seconds. i was in awe but at the same time felt starnge. btw, i don't drink or do drugs; i'm a health professional and instructor. no one knows about this, including my husband,even though i tell him everything. and i don't really know why i did not tell him about the incident i experienced.
